beer.beer_description: Fresh from the Akasha studio comes this tropical bomb blast of Hopic Thunder! starring the experimental HBC 586 hop.  It’s an epic mash up of lychee and mango characters with classic resinous undertones, in a West Coast-inspired take that goes full Pale Ale in glorious style.
